{"type": "article", "id": 28545, "title": "巧克力包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-22T06:53:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702172703BW1Crw4tUVosxjLk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://rice-creative.com/\">Rice Creative</a> 最近接受了越南巧克力品牌 Marou 的委托，为其与新加坡国家美术馆（The National Gallery Singapore）的合作款设计了一套融合了美术馆建筑特色与越南传统版画工艺的包装。设计师们将美术馆三种不同的空间分别与巧克力的口味一一对应，设计出了三款图标。这些图标不仅出现在黑金配色的外壳左右两侧，还采用传统的 Đông Hồ 版画工艺由工匠手工印在桑皮纸包装上，过程中所使用到的染料均由当地的植物与贝壳制成。作为一款放在美术馆里销售的巧克力，包装本身就是一件承载了传统的艺术品。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172701N1UEWhlmkoQtr7qw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172702xWs5KqOD7PCZEN9z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021727029sfBSdXabAmiVglI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702172703Z4XpiJqPTAGEYbnS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}